Like, with Stefanie,
it has been way harder.

00:40:22.360 --> 00:40:23.110
KAKI KING: Really?

00:40:23.110 --> 00:40:23.710
GIORGIA LUPI: It is.

00:40:23.710 --> 00:40:24.340
Oh, my god, yes.

00:40:24.340 --> 00:40:24.990
You have no idea.

00:40:24.990 --> 00:40:26.080
KAKI KING: She's talking
crap about her ex.

00:40:26.080 --> 00:40:26.900
GIORGIA LUPI: We have.

00:40:26.900 --> 00:40:27.400
[LAUGHTER]

00:40:27.400 --> 00:40:28.020
No, no.

00:40:28.020 --> 00:40:29.560
We share this on stage as well.

00:40:29.560 --> 00:40:31.000
Stefanie and I
arrived to a point

00:40:31.000 --> 00:40:33.080
where we really needed
to have a shared

00:40:33.080 --> 00:40:35.140
spreadsheet of the
things that we hated

00:40:35.140 --> 00:40:38.260
about each other's design so
